Package gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameOver
    Class for the game over screen, displays small animation, the winning players name and a close button.
    GUI
    Class for creating the main window handling all input including mouse, keys.
    Menu
    Class for creating the menu to the game which allows the user to select connection port through the use of swing.
    UltimateDijkstras
    Implements a varied version of Dijkstra's algorithm, getting a path from one tile to another using the 8 locations around the players current location.
